item.title: Kim Mitchell
item.description: Joseph Kim Mitchell is a Canadian musician. He was the lead singer and guitarist for the band Max Webster before going on to a solo career. His 1984 single, 'Go For Soda', was his only charted song on the US Billboard Hot 100, reaching number 86. Several other singles such as 'Patio Lanterns', 'Rock and Roll Duty', and 'Rockland Wonderland', reached the top 20 in Canada.
